</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="07AF96B5FFFEFFD0F5246366FE0ECCC2" box="[113,453,881,905]" pageId="26" pageNumber="261" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="4F0AC53EFFFEFFD0F5246366FE0ECCC2" blockId="26.[111,647,304,905]" box="[113,453,881,905]" pageId="26" pageNumber="261">VERNACULAR NAME. — Voane sila.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="07AF96B5FFFEFFD0F52463A5FE51CA6C" pageId="26" pageNumber="261" type="description">
<paragraph id="4F0AC53EFFFEFFD0F52463A5FEC9CC82" blockId="26.[111,648,945,1319]" box="[113,258,945,971]" pageId="26" pageNumber="261">DESCRIPTION</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4F0AC53EFFFEFFD0F52463C5FE51CA6C" blockId="26.[111,648,945,1319]" pageId="26" pageNumber="261">
Large trees. Twigs angular, glabrous; terminal buds glabrous. Leaves 6-16 × 
<quantity id="884D68DBFFFEFFD0F4E563E4FDCBCB41" box="[432,512,1008,1034]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" metricValueMax="7.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="26" pageNumber="261" unit="cm" value="5.0" valueMax="7.0" valueMin="3.0">3-7 cm</quantity>
, alternate or somewhat clustered, stiffly chartaceous, elliptic or obovate-elliptic, base acute often lamina shortly decurrent on the petiole, apex obtuse; lateral veins inconspicuous, 6-8; upper surface smooth, lower surface with rather lax, raised reticulation; margin often slightly inrolled; domatia lacking. Flowers unknown. Infructescences 
<quantity id="884D68DBFFFEFFD0F4C464DAFE16CBA3" box="[401,477,1230,1256]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="26" pageNumber="261" unit="cm" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3-4 cm</quantity>
long. Fruits not seen. Cupule deeply cup-shaped, 
<quantity id="884D68DBFFFEFFD0F49D64F9FDDBCA43" box="[456,528,1261,1288]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.8" pageId="26" pageNumber="261" unit="cm" value="1.8">1.8 cm</quantity>
wide, 
<quantity id="884D68DBFFFEFFD0F70764F9FD4ECA43" box="[594,645,1261,1288]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="26" pageNumber="261" unit="cm" value="1.0">1 cm</quantity>
deep, with persistent tepals.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
